<p n="1"> <!-- ged: this is stll part of the 1st parpagraph from page 1-->
<ln n="15"/><unclear reason="no idea">found</unclear> with due caution
<ln n="16"/>Lot of wild drivers on 
<ln n="17"/>the road 
<closer> 
    <ln n="18" />M. Warren.
</closer>
</p>
<p n="2"> <!-- am: Fathers letter on the back of the page-->
    <ln n="1"/><car>Duesenberg</car> ran beautifully -so far!
    <ln n="2"/>First day <weather>nice weather</weather>;<underline>very</underline> <weather>cold</weather>
    <ln n="3"/>yesterday. You may need your coon
    <ln n="4"/>coat, heavy hat or fur cap!!
    <ln n="5"/>Look forward to our <language langID="German">Wiedersehen</language>. <!-- ged: This is a German word that means "meet again" --> 
</p>    
<closer>
    <ln n="1"/>Faithfully
    <ln n="2"/>Father.
</closer>
